Format DB - Running on CodeIgniter 2.1 Reactor, PHP 5.3.x
=========================================================

Installation
-------------------------------
I suggest you drop it into your third_party folder and load it 
that way.  Otherwise, you can just copy the files into the library and config 
directories.


Basic Instructions
-------------------------------
View them online at the following address
http://www.eclarian.com/codeigniter-format-database-library/



Bug Reports
-------------------------------
If you run across a bug, feel free to email us at 
eclarian[at]eclarian[dot]com